      <step><![CDATA[squeeze the ginger through a muslin into the ginger, rice wine. Keep 1 tsp of the ginger]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[Deep fry the chicken, then stir fry with the dried mushrooms, 20s]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[Add hoisin sauce, yellow bean paste, stir until warm, serve.]]></step>
